President Obama endorsed Joe Biden for president in this web video released Tuesday.
"I'm so proud to endorse Joe Biden to be president of the United States," President Obama said.
"Choosing Joe to be my vice president was one of the best decisions I ever made, and he became a good friend.
"With President Obama on our team, we’re going to unite our party and restore the soul of the nation.
I’m proud to endorse my friend @JoeBiden for President of the United States.